<section class="pg-section" data-section="About Laser Facials">
  <h2 class="pg-h">About Laser Facials</h2>
  <p class="pg-text">It is an FDA approved non-surgical procedure that tightens skin, smoothens lines and wrinkles around the eyes, mouth, neck and chest to restore a youthful, healthy looking appearance.</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Laser facial can also be used to treat problematic areas, such as acne scars, sun damage, age spots, and much more.</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Our laser treatments are safe and effective even for thin and delicate areas of the skin such as face, neck and décolleté. It is based on a unique method of energy dispersion, emitting narrow pulse widths with multiple peaks of energy, resulting in more effective treatment.</p>
</section>

<section class="pg-section" data-section="See Our Before &amp; After Results">
  <img class="pg-img" src="/images/651c7c197b52.png" alt="k.1757_serene_relaxing_nature_very_slight_purple_hue_very_relax_f9c18564-0ba0-42a6-8e7c-27" width="1440" height="547" loading="lazy" />
  <h2 class="pg-h">See Our Before &amp; After Results</h2>
  <p class="pg-text">Amazing transformation from laser facial treatments! This real before &amp; after comparison shows the dramatic wrinkle reduction our clients achieve, especially around the delicate under-eye area. See how our advanced  ClearLift laser technology can turn back the clock on aging - the results speak for themselves!</p>
  <img class="pg-img" src="/images/180e95701089.png" alt="7D71E48E-3AF9-4A1B-8E0F-E50F9FB324F6.png" width="600" height="600" loading="lazy" />
  <img class="pg-img" src="/images/f260f818780a.png" alt="1A35DCD1-0FD1-414F-98E6-4799B756AB15.png" width="668" height="376" loading="lazy" />
</section>

<section class="pg-section" data-section="Why Choose ClearLift in at Menon Medispa in Millburn?">
  <h2 class="pg-h">Why Choose ClearLift in at Menon Medispa in Millburn?</h2>
  <p class="pg-text">Experience the most advanced, comfortable, and effective skin rejuvenation treatment available. Here's what sets ClearLift apart from other options.</p>
  <h3 class="pg-h">Zero Downtime Required</h3>
  <p class="pg-text">Unlike traditional lasers or chemical peels, ClearLift allows you to return to all activities immediately after treatment.</p>
  <h3 class="pg-h">Completely Pain-Free</h3>
  <p class="pg-text">Experience gentle warming sensations instead of pain. No numbing cream or anesthesia needed for comfortable treatment.</p>
  <h3 class="pg-h">Quick 30-Minute Sessions</h3>
  <p class="pg-text">Fit your skin transformation into your busy schedule with efficient treatments during your lunch break.</p>
  <img class="pg-img" src="/images/bf60da9a2083.jpg" alt="" width="480" height="270" loading="lazy" />
  <p class="pg-text">Watch how this innovative treatment can transform your lips while maintaining their natural beauty.</p>
  <h3 class="pg-h">Safe for All Skin Types</h3>
  <p class="pg-text">ClearLift works safely on all six Fitzpatrick skin types, including darker skin tones that other treatments can't address.</p>
  <h3 class="pg-h">FDA-Approved Technology</h3>
  <p class="pg-text">ClearLift uses clinically proven Q-switched laser technology, backed by extensive research and safety studies.</p>
  <h3 class="pg-h">Long-Lasting Results</h3>
  <p class="pg-text">Results improve over time as your skin naturally produces more collagen, with effects lasting up to 2 years.</p>
  <h3 class="pg-h">Beyond Facial Rejuvination</h3>
  <p class="pg-text">ClearLift laser technology offers remarkable results for lip enhancement and rejuvenation. This gentle, non-invasive treatment stimulates collagen production in the delicate lip area, naturally improving lip definition, reducing fine lines around the mouth, and restoring a fuller, more youthful appearance.</p>
  <p class="pg-text">The precision of ClearLift allows us to treat the lip borders and surrounding area without downtime, making it an ideal solution for those seeking subtle, natural lip enhancement without fillers.</p>
</section>

